General.Name: Kshitij Polyline Limited
General.Description: Kshitij Polyline Limited manufactures, distributes, and supplies lamination equipment and stationery products in India. The company offers plastic card holders, binding materials, plastic files and folders, face shield masks, metal clip fittings and accessories, personalized products, file folder accessories, neck lanyards, badge clip fittings, plastic clip fittings and other accessories, industrial plastic sheets, lamination materials, plastic sheets, and miscellaneous products. It also exports its products to various countries, such as Uganda, Lebanon, Sri Lanka, South Africa, Bhutan, Nepal, Dubai, and internationally. The company was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India.
